00:52:05.280 --> 00:52:08.820
I'm like, you're telling me this like two days before I'm supposed to go speak to these people.

00:52:08.820 --> 00:52:11.840
Like what exactly are you expecting me to do, right?

00:52:12.500 --> 00:52:24.320
So again, like for somebody that's trying to show a demo of, I don't know, let's say I'm trying to show a demo of Azure or whatever it is if there's no connectivity.

00:52:24.320 --> 00:52:26.120
It makes a demo a little bit hard to do.

